OL,3,CSeventh arrest in investigation into
OL,4,Cdeath of man in Carlisle
OL,6,FA seventh person has been arrested in
OL,7,Fconnection with the death of a man in
OL,8,FCarlisle.
OL,10,FInvestigations are ongoing into the
OL,11,Fdeath of the man, aged in his 40s,
OL,12,Ffollowing an incident at a property on
OL,13,FWhinsmoor Drive on 30 May.
OL,15,FOfficers received a report that a man
OL,16,Fhad suffered a serious head injury and
OL,17,Fhe was taken by air ambulance to Royal
OL,18,FVictoria Infirmary in Newcastle.
OL,20,FHe later died on 2 June and Cumbria
OL,21,FPolice launched a murder inquiry.
