OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1780989358
OL,3,CSeventh arrest in investigation into
OL,4,Cdeath of man in Carlisle
OL,6,FAn initial six people were arrested in
OL,7,Fconnection with this incident on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of a number of offences,
OL,9,Fincluding grievous bodily harm and
OL,10,Fmurder.
OL,12,FNow a seventh individual has been
OL,13,Farrested on suspicion of grievous
OL,14,Fbodily harm with intent.
OL,16,FAll individuals have since been
OL,17,Freleased on bail and police enquiries
OL,18,Fare ongoing.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/3
