OL,3,CSeventh arrest in investigation into
OL,4,Cdeath of man in Carlisle
OL,6,FAnyone who witnessed this incident, or
OL,7,Fwho has any information relating to it
OL,8,Fin the hours and days leading up to
OL,9,Fit, is urged to come forward.
OL,11,FAnyone with CCTV or dashcam footage in
OL,12,Fthe areas of Whinsmoor Drive and
OL,13,FCentral Avenue is being encouraged to
OL,14,Fcontact police.
